{"tid":2242335,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"環球網：蔡英文違反國安法 台灣公然勾結外國勢力","createTime":"2020-10-14T03:14:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-14T06:59:27.000Z","uid":337052,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"remark":"[gold]⚠️ 管理團隊警示：本主題已被回報為「標題真實性有待確定，可能含有誤導或虛假資訊」，請各位留意。[/gold]\n警示措拖說明：https://lih.kg/eobQbT","replies":[{"pid":"73f571dfa4234f61bfcedf4631dcd9894f0c8e1f","tid":2242335,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T03:14:19.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">公開秘密首次曝光？蔡英文視察樂山雷達站，身後出現美國人的臉</span></strong><br />\n來源：環球網<br />\n<br />\n2020-10-14 10:42<br />\n<br />\n【環球網報導記者趙友平】<span class=\"red\">台灣當局領導人蔡英文昨日（13日）到海拔高度2620公尺（米）的樂山雷達站視察，台媒稱，在台灣&ldquo;總統府&rdquo;公佈的視察片中出現了美方人員，這也是民進黨當局首度公開美方人員進駐樂山站。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://rs1.huanqiucdn.cn/dp/api/images/imageDir/df6f4e6c620457c4c9d44a5f447fdbf5u1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs1.huanqiucdn.cn%2Fdp%2Fapi%2Fimages%2FimageDir%2Fdf6f4e6c620457c4c9d44a5f447fdbf5u1.png&h=f017c0e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蔡英文視察樂山雷達站，照片中可見有美方人員跟隨。圖源：台灣中時新聞網<br />\n<br />\n據台灣&ldquo;ETtoday新聞雲&rdquo;報導，<span class=\"red\">蔡英文13日進入樂山雷達站長程預警雷達機房，當時這名蓄平頭的美方人員就在一行人身後，有美軍方安全人員的架勢。</span>報導稱，雖然美方長駐樂山雷達站屬公開的秘密，但外界從未見當地美方人員公開露面，&ldquo;軍媒鏡頭&lsquo;驚鴻一瞥&rsquo;，為此事留下左證&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n台灣中時新聞網則稱，蔡英文視察屬高度機密，由於&ldquo;總統府&rdquo;公佈軍事視察片有嚴謹的審核流程，<span class=\"red\">13日播出的美方人員出現在樂山的畫面，代表民進黨當局有意釋放出台美軍事合作緊密關係，共同分享最機敏的導彈預警情報。</span><br />\n<br />\n樂山雷達站位於新竹五峰鄉，部署了美國&ldquo;鋪路爪&rdquo;遠程預警雷達，台灣&ldquo;自由時報&rdquo;稱，這是台軍重要的偵蒐系統之一。蔡英文13日在臉書上也將樂山雷達站稱為&ldquo;台灣空防的眼睛&rdquo;。她聲稱，樂山雷達站負責導彈預警工作，只要周邊地區發射導彈、火箭，都能第一時間偵測到。"},{"pid":"7fe1d10f3be2536b6b772de37044ccdab72ef975","tid":2242335,"uid":337052,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T03:17:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/08/25/phpKcgrIm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F08%2F25%2FphpKcgrIm.jpg&h=81cc44b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nAIT今天PO出近年美台合作的照片，圖為「前美軍飛行員和維修人員組成美國技術協助團隊，2016年起為台灣軍隊提供訓練與諮詢」。（圖取自AIT臉書）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3271332\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3271332&d=Tp8cMPEgSVVC2rtXaxUH2uDrFCZ%2FFQqiuLijmhCLlc8%3D&h=1938d2fb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3271332&h=abcf6c65\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3271332</a>"},{"pid":"ce1cb421fbdd6ef63b47cb91a700cfa50e88cabf","tid":2242335,"uid":8257,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T03:18:20.000Z","msg":"白人一定係美國人?"},{"pid":"25331dbbd11447a05a341401ffe50d394585da9b","tid":2242335,"uid":123395,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T03:19:45.000Z","msg":"咁咪去台灣拉人囉"},{"pid":"c6f94264406f95be6981f4fef7f2efa800945e17","tid":2242335,"uid":22210,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T03:20:17.000Z","msg":"嗯 咁去台灣拉人未<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24c5786d0c86732c3bb15f1ecc278adec121a096","tid":2242335,"uid":256246,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T03:20:39.000Z","msg":"侵違反咗好耐啦，幾時拉侵呀"},{"pid":"535979ba5c3d79c99212b632a3117561a5564eed","tid":2242335,"uid":72228,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"25331dbbd11447a05a341401ffe50d394585da9b","tid":2242335,"uid":123395,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T03:19:45.000Z","msg":"咁咪去台灣拉人囉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T03:21:01.000Z","msg":"呢個真<br />\n武統台灣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a97c311f8ccb439ceeeeee2144cf1e0ade799523","tid":22